OL,2,M" A Farewell to PAL" The analogue
OL,4,Mcolour TV system
OL,6,CRoger Dealtry
OL,7,CSun 14:00-14:30
OL,8,CStage B
OL,10,GThis is a talk on the PAL (System I)
OL,11,Gcolour television standard. Something
OL,12,Gthat was once used in every home in
OL,13,Gthe UK, but now with the advent of
OL,14,Gdigital broadcasting has quietly
OL,15,Gslipped into the pages of history. It
OL,16,Gdeserves one final fanfare and who
OL,17,Gbetter to give it some love than the
OL,18,GEMF community. We're going to marvel
OL,19,Gat the sheer engineering ingenuity of
OL,20,Gthe PAL system at a fairly technical
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
